precis:
Amendment to the UNITED STATES TARIFF RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS which
corrects an anomaly in section XV of the Schedule to permit FTA tariff
preference to be granted to goods provided that at least 50% of the value
of the goods is of FTA origin and to allow FTA tariff preferences to be
granted to such goods as ranges, radiators and barbecues.
